quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  36,71,"Awa lam yaraw anna khalaqnalahum mimma AAamilat aydeena anAAaman fahumlaha malikoon"
  36,72,"Wathallalnaha lahumfaminha rakoobuhum waminha ya/kuloon"
  36,73,"Walahum feeha manafiAAu wamasharibuafala yashkuroon"
  36,74,"Wattakhathoo min dooni Allahialihatan laAAallahum yunsaroon"
  36,75,"La yastateeAAoona nasrahumwahum lahum jundun muhdaroon"
  36,76,"Fala yahzunka qawluhum innanaAAlamu ma yusirroona wama yuAAlinoon"
  36,77,"Awa lam yara al-insanu annakhalaqnahu min nutfatin fa-itha huwa khaseemunmubeen"
  36,78,"Wadaraba lana mathalanwanasiya khalqahu qala man yuhyee alAAithamawahiya rameem"
  36,79,"Qul yuhyeeha allatheeanshaaha awwala marratin wahuwa bikulli khalqin AAaleem"
  36,80,"Allathee jaAAala lakum mina ashshajarial-akhdari naran fa-itha antum minhutooqidoon"
  36,81,"Awa laysa allathee khalaqa assamawatiwal-arda biqadirin AAala an yakhluqamithlahum bala wahuwa alkhallaqu alAAaleem"
  36,82,"Innama amruhu itha aradashay-an an yaqoola lahu kun fayakoon"
  36,83,"Fasubhana allathee biyadihimalakootu kulli shay-in wa-ilayhi turjaAAoon"
